  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3-Hour Power Cuts from 16th \u2013 19th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) approved power cuts of 3-Hours from 16th -19th August as follows;",
        "Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekara said that the daily power outage had to be extended for 3-Hours due to the breakdown in Unit 1 of the Norochcholai Power Plant.",
        "\"Technical staff is working to identify the fault. Unit 2 is undergoing scheduled maintenance work. Unit 3 will continue to operate,\" he tweeted.",
        "The Minister said that West Coast & other Fuel Power Plants will be used to manage the supply.",
        "Chinese Research / Survey Vessel Yuan Wang 5 reaches Sri Lanka\u2019s Hambantota"
      ],
